  "title": "HR & Admin Executive #JTL",
  "description": "<ul><li>Datamining and profiling of potential international candidates; create database for easy references. </li></ul><ul><li>Liaise with School’s HR and Shared Services team to advance Faculty appointment, re-appointment, promotion and tenure and related processes and ensure smooth execution of administrative process. </li></ul><ul><li>Provide end to end support on faculty recruitment such as (but not limited to) interview / meeting scheduling, travel arrangement, campus visit and claims </li></ul><ul><li>Support preparation of faculty dossier in appointment, re-appointment, promotion for Committee’s review and to ensure timely submission of documentation and compliance with University policies. </li></ul><ul><li>Support annual faculty appraisal exercise to ensure adherence to timelines and processes. </li></ul><ul><li>Maintain up-to-date records and assist in the preparation of reports, presentations, and internal communication materials </li></ul><ul><li>Perform any other faculty-related duties as assigned to support the team’s and school’s objectives. </li></ul><ul><li>Serve as key support to school management for faculty recruitment-related publicity materials. </li></ul><p><strong>Requirements </strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma or Degree in Business Administration or Business Management </li><li>Preferably with 2-3 years of relevant experiences </li><li>Proficient in MS Office </li></ul><p><strong>Interested candidates please send in your resume to:</strong></p><p><strong>Topaz Liang Huimin (CEI No. R1104500), email to: topaz@recruitexpress.com.sg </strong><br /><strong>EA License No: 99C4599</strong></p><p></p>",
